### **CSS**

```css
.top-nav {
  position: sticky;        /* stays visible while scrolling */
  top: 0;
  background-color: #d9e6ef;   /* pale blue, calm signal color */
  padding: 0.5rem 0;
  text-align: center;
  z-index: 10;
